Document: RetargetModifier3D
Path: godot/classes/class_retargetmodifier3d.rst
Summary: Defines a modifier for retargeting bone transformations in Godot's animation system.

Inherits: RefCounted < Object

RetargetModifier3D is an abstract base class for modifiers that retarget bone transformations. It is used within the AnimationRetargeting resource to define how bone poses from one skeleton should be mapped to another.

This class itself does not perform any retargeting. Instead, it serves as a base for specific retargeting strategies. You will typically use subclasses like RetargetingModifier3D or RetargetingModifier3D.
