Path: godot/classes/class_retargetmodifier3d.rst
Summary: This section details the methods and enumerations for controlling transform retargeting in RetargetModifier3D.

Methods
Method: is_position_enabled() → bool
Checks if position retargeting is enabled.
Method: is_rotation_enabled() → bool
Checks if rotation retargeting is enabled.
Method: is_scale_enabled() → bool
Checks if scale retargeting is enabled.
Method: set_position_enabled(enabled: bool) → void
Enables or disables position retargeting.
Method: set_rotation_enabled(enabled: bool) → void
Enables or disables rotation retargeting.
Method: set_scale_enabled(enabled: bool) → void
Enables or disables scale retargeting.

Enumerations
enum TransformFlag:
  TRANSFORM_FLAG_POSITION = 1
    If set, allows to retarget the position.
  TRANSFORM_FLAG_ROTATION = 2
    If set, allows to retarget the rotation.
  TRANSFORM_FLAG_SCALE = 4
    If set, allows to retarget the scale.
  TRANSFORM_FLAG_ALL = 7
    If set, allows to retarget the position/rotation/scale.
